dct_title_s: [Hobart] : southern metropolitan area / produced in the office of the Southern Metropolitan Master Planning Authority (5171-D)
dct_description_sm: Relief shown by contours at 20-foot intervals. Depth shown by soundings. These maps are from a series covering Hobart and environs. Maps show buildings, roads and road names, and cadastral boundaries without identification. Includes index to adjoining sheets. Sheets lack coordinates.
dct_creator_sm: Tasmania. Southern Metropolitan Master Planning Authority
dct_publisher_sm: Hobart : Southern Metropolitan Master Planning Authority, 1964.
